    "IntroductionGenerative models are increasingly used.",
    "They have demonstrated a great deal of success in generating highquality fake photographs, videos and audios, which may frequently be impossible to be distinguished from the genuine ones.",
    "The Internet makes it possible for anybody to create this type of media.",
    "The use of deep learning algorithms to the production of this form of content is a significant contributor to the development of the notion known as ''deepfake''.",
    "A person with malicious intentions is able to create real-time video deepfakes using the tools that are currently available."
